   <narrative xml:lang="EN">For GGF funds will support Ecoceanos&apos; work in strengthening the citizens monitoring and resistance to the salmon farming industry in the Chilean Patagonia. Large scale aquiculture is drastically altering the livelihoods of coastal communities in the region as it simultaneously deteriorates water quality, coastal habitats, and the health of wildlife in the area. Ecoceanos will work to create more local opposition to the industry, communicate the long term effects of the industry&apos;s current practices, and research the diseases that spurn from the aquaculture practices in Patagonian waters.</narrative>
